### packages/registry-server/

| Source area | Documentation |
|---|---|
| `lib/registry-service.js`, `scripts/build-db-spec.js`, `shared/spec/` | `.cursor/skills/qv-registry-autobase-patterns/` |

## What to do

When a change touches APIs, schemas, signatures, file paths, or behavior documented in the map above:

1. Read the corresponding documentation file
2. Check if the change invalidates any documented information
3. If it does, suggest updating the doc — or update it directly if the scope is small
